downloadTitle: SBR and Digipoort support in Microsoft Dynamics AX - Netherlands (NL)
downloadDescription: ​This white paper describes the country-specific update released for the Netherlands related to submission of VAT and ICP declaration in XBRL format via Digipoort services.
detailsSection: ​The aim of the document is to provide Dutch companies and other stakeholders with the description of the functionality, setup overview, and main steps for the reports creation and filing to the authority.This document contains also general information about SBR program and requirements for direct submission via Digipoort services.
